      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MARINA BAY (5) has a strong record this track and trip with four wins and three placings from 11 starts. Scored by 3.5 lengths last time (16.61) in a Grade 5 over 300m at this track. Rates on top and should go close. WEATHER MAN RICK (1) is boxed nicely on the inside. Latest effort finished last over 300m at this track beaten 6 lengths (17.07) behind Piper Beach in a Grade 5 on March 9. Suited here and expected to run well. EXHIBIT (3) turned in a solid run last start over 300m at this track finishing 4th and beaten only 2.25 lengths (16.75). Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from four starts. Has ability and is one of the better chances. GLASS BULLET (6) is right in the mix.",
